So we're just going to line it up.

00:04:16.519 --> 00:04:17.519
OK.

00:04:17.519 --> 00:04:23.560
So now, I'm just going to folded it over.

00:04:23.560 --> 00:04:29.590
I'm going to fold it pass the brown blanket
because like I said, I like to see like I

00:04:29.590 --> 00:04:37.990
like to make sure all three colors are showing
when the bed is made because they all matched

00:04:37.990 --> 00:04:38.990
so nicely.

00:04:38.990 --> 00:04:39.990
All right.

00:04:39.990 --> 00:04:50.430
So now, I can just start tucking in the comforter.

00:04:50.430 --> 00:04:57.600
OK.

00:04:57.600 --> 00:05:03.120
So now that that's tucked in I'm just going
to quickly fold the blankets, then we'll grab

00:05:03.120 --> 00:05:04.560
the pillows, and then we'll be done.

00:05:04.560 --> 00:05:05.560
All right.

