So I put the pillows on the bed.

00:05:09.900 --> 00:05:15.370
This is going to sound really weird but I
put the pillows so the close side of the pillow

00:05:15.370 --> 00:05:20.090
case is showing as opposed to the open part
just because it looks neater.

00:05:20.090 --> 00:05:22.520
And yeah, it just looks neater and cleaner.

